    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235020/extras/78de1b5f0e9e83cac07df13327fef94f.avif?t=1768650931\" width=800 height=56 /></span>DEMO FEATURING: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 mouse-wrecking levels  (+ Endless Mode)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 friendly Cell types </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 10+ upgrade types </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 4 unique viruses to defeat </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and MORE!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE GAME:</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235020/extras/2b3717911eac6f68dd0a1b0c3c71285d.poster.avif?t=1768650931\" width=800 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235020/extras/2b3717911eac6f68dd0a1b0c3c71285d.webm?t=1768650931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235020/extras/2b3717911eac6f68dd0a1b0c3c71285d.mp4?t=1768650931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Affordable Healthcare blends rapid clicking action with relaxing resource management mechanics to deliver a captivating experience. Your primary objective is to safeguard cells from the onslaught of malicious viruses. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your weapon of choice? Your trusty mouse, of course! Click on the viruses to eliminate them before they can wreak havoc on the cells. But be warned: the viruses won't go down without a fight. Some are faster, while others are tougher to defeat. You'll need to stay alert and react swiftly to keep the cells safe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235020/extras/758a643a8093d5c3f9ae190f5e7a78a7.avif?t=1768650931\" width=800 height=143 /></span>Because nothing fixes a systemic issue quite like throwing money at it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > By keeping cells alive, you earn coins which can be invested in upgrades to boost your clicking power, automate defenses with White Blood Cells. Completing levels will earn you more and more DNA points to spend in a expansive Skill Tree!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235020/extras/2b2822f227d44084bf3036334957cfba.avif?t=1768650931\" width=800 height=90 /></span></p>",
